comments: Portis (MIL) legally contests Vukcevic's (WAS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
There is no clear and conclusive evidence that confirms that Gill (WAS) is not the last player to touch ball before it goes OOB.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly brings his right arm toward Gill's (WAS) back and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo attempts to step around Gill after his gather.
Connaughton (MIL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Avdija's (WAS) arms as he makes clean contact with the ball.
Portis (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball prior to incidental arm contact occurring with Gill (WAS) at the end of the drive.

Although Gill (IND) is in the restricted area when he and Connaughton (MIL) come together, he is not attempting to draw an offensive foul and Connaughton does not take a direct line to the basket when marginal contact occurs between the two players.
Poole (WAS) legally dislodges the ball away as incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Avdija (WAS) briefly gets a hand on the ball prior to incidental follow-through body contact occurring with Connaughton (MIL) as he secures the rebound.
Gill (WAS) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Gill (WAS) moves alongside Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path before absorbing the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Avdija (WAS) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Middleton's (MIL) right arm after the release.
Connaughton (MIL) reaches at the ball and incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Gill (WAS) during his shot attempt near the basket.
Poole (WAS) briefly brings his hands on Middleton's (MIL) back as he pursues the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
